    <section id="about">
        <h2>About VukaUp</h2>
        <p>VukaUp is a digital platform designed to empower South African youth and adults by providing access to education, skills development, and career opportunities.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="problem">
        <h2>Problem</h2>
        <p>High youth unemployment in South Africa limits economic growth and social mobility. VukaUp aims to address this issue by streamlining the process of finding relevant opportunities.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="solution">
        <h2>Solution</h2>
        <p>VukaUp offers a secure platform for users to create personalized profiles, access AI-powered matching for opportunities, and save time by eliminating the need to search through multiple platforms.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="target">
        <h2>Target Market</h2>
        <p>VukaUp targets South African youth and adults seeking education, skills development, and career advancement opportunities.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="advantage">
        <h2>Competitive Advantage</h2>
        <p>VukaUp differentiates itself through its comprehensive platform, AI-powered matching, integration with learning platforms, and focus on user privacy.</p>
    </section>

